  "description": "A long exposure photograph capturing a scenic view of a bridge spanning across a body of water, likely a bay or strait, under a vibrant, warm-toned sky. The sky is ablaze with oranges, yellows, and some shades of purple from the setting sun. The bridge is a suspension bridge, with visible towers and cables, silhouetted against the bright sky. A small landmass or island is visible on the left side with what appears to be a small structure on it.  The water surface is relatively calm, exhibiting subtle ripples. Distant hills or mountains form the backdrop. A long, narrow structure, possibly a pier or breakwater, extends into the water from the foreground. The overall scene evokes a sense of tranquility and grandeur.",
